casebody.data:
TOWNSHIP OF WILLIAMSTOWN, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
SANDALWOOD RANCH, LLC, Alec Kolenda, and Sarah Kolenda, Defendants-Appellants,
and
Love Advertising, Inc., Defendant. SC: 158171
COA: 337469 Supreme Court of Michigan. May 22, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the August 7, 2018 judgment of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court.
